title: Amy Coney Barrett, Florida Rep. Waltz
itunes:title: Amy Coney Barrett, Florida Rep. Waltz
description:
Guests: Russell Wheeler, Visiting Fellow at the Brookings Institution, Ellen Hughes-Cromwick, Senior Resident Fellow for the Climate and Energy Program at Third Way, and former Chief Economist for Ford Motor Company, Frank Maisano, Partner at Bracewell’s Policy Resolution Group, Max Burns, Democratic Strategist, and Congressman Michael Waltz, a Republican representing Florida's 6th district.
